text: Major General M. A. Matin is a Bangladeshi military official and politician. He was elected as MP of Magura-1 in Third General Election of Bangladesh and Fourth General Election of Bangladesh. ==References== Category:People from Magura District Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Bengali politicians Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Bangladesh Army generals Category:Possibly living people Category:Year of birth missing
